// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2089 — Mass File Rename (alphv)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ca463609-aa81-510d-81ba-9067c60c2784

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
